<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4577102>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 2. Habitus of holotype of Pseudogaurax striatus, new species (female, specimen ZRC_BDP0021667). A, lateral habitus showing thoracic pleura, head, legs and wing, note the stripe at the bottom margin of the anepisternum; B, dorsal habitus. Note extended terminalia on both A and B." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4577102/files/figure.png" .

